'''xerophyte'''

#{{botany}}: Any [[plant]] suited for life in a [[habitat]] where [[water]] is [[scarce]], such as in a [[desert]] or [[chaparral]]. Such plants may be [[succulent]], have small or [[reduce]]d [[leaves]], or [[spine]]s.
